  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Promoting Ethical Recruitment and Employment of Migrant Workers in Agricultural Supply Chains in Thailand by Piloting Blockchain Solutions</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">IOM partnered with Diginex Solutions, an environmental, social and governance (ESG) data infrastructure company, to test how and if block chain can make supply chain monitoring and management easier, and migrant workers&apos; lives safer. During a pilot project, IOM and Diginex Solutions will test eMin - an existing digital tool that allows migrant workers to share information about their employment conditions, recruitment experiences and the migration-associated costs.</narrative>
  </description>
